      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GARY INDIANA (1) has mixed form recently, finishing fourth (23.48) in a Grade 5 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. This looks easier and expected to bounce back. TARAWI QUEENIE (7) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (23.31) at this track behind Kalani Sea in a Grade 5. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. The form out of her last race has been franked. Bold showing expected. MR. SPECKLE (8) turned in a modest effort most recently when fifth at Maitland over 400m behind Despicable Kyro (23.18) in a Grade 5. Scored at his previous run. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from eight attempts. Has ability and can measure up. SUDDENLY I SEE (2) looks an each-way chance.",
